Scripts
=======

orcatk_pairwise.pl
------------------
Under the scripts directory, the orcatk_pairwise.pl script performs the basic
pairwise analysis.

For orcatk_pairwise.pl usage, run the script without any arguments.

orcatk_phastcons.pl
------------------
The orcatk_phastCons.pl script performs a similar analysis to
orcatk_pairwise.pl, however, instead of computing a pairwise alignment and
a conservation profile, it instead directly extracts a phastCons score profile.

For orcatk_phastCons.pl usage, run the script without any arguments.

orcatk_aligner.pl
-----------------
Align two DNA sequences using progressive global alignment.

For orcatk_aligner.pl usage, run the script without any arguments.
